\lim _{x \rightarrow 0}\left(\sec ^{2} x\right)^{\frac{1}{x^{2}}}=\lim _{x \rightarrow 0}\left(1+\tan ^{2} x\right)^{\frac{1}{x^{2}}} 
=\mathrm{e}^{\lim\limits _{x \rightarrow 0} \frac{1}{x^{2}} \tan ^{2} x}=\mathrm{e}^{\lim\limits _{x \rightarrow 0} \frac{x^{2}}{x^{2}}}=\mathrm{e}^{1}=\mathrm{e}.
