<p>求 <m>\displaystyle\lim _{x \rightarrow 0} \frac{\left(1+x^{2}\right)^{\frac{1}{3}}-1}{\cos x-1} </m>.</p>

<p>解 <m>\because x \rightarrow 0 </m> 时, <m> \sqrt[3]{1+x^{2}}-1 \sim \frac{1}{3} x^{2}, 1-\cos x \sim \frac{1}{2} x^{2}</m>,
\ltme\gt
\therefore \lim _{x \rightarrow 0} \frac{\left(1+x^{2}\right)^{\frac{1}{3}}-1}{\cos x-1}=\lim _{x \rightarrow 0} \frac{\frac{1}{3} x^{2}}{-\frac{1}{2} x^{2}}=-\frac{2}{3} 
\lt/me\gt</p>

<p>解 <m>\displaystyle\lim _{x \rightarrow 0} \frac{\sqrt{1+x \sin x}-1}{\mathrm{e}^{x^{2}}-1}=\lim _{x \rightarrow 0} \frac{\frac{x \sin x}{2}}{x^{2}}=\frac{1}{2}</m>.</p>

<p>解 <m>\displaystyle\lim _{x \rightarrow 0} \frac{\ln \left(1+x^{2}\right) \cdot \arcsin 3 x}{\left(\mathrm{e}^{x}-1\right)^{2} \tan 5 x}=\lim _{x \rightarrow 0} \frac{x^{2} \cdot 3 x}{x^{2} \cdot 5 x}=\frac{3}{5}</m>.</p>

<p>若当 <m>x \rightarrow 0</m> 时, <m>\tan x-\sin x </m> 与 <m> a \sin ^{3} x </m> 是等价无穷小,则 <m> a=</m>____.</p>

<p>解 
\ltme\gt
\begin{aligned}
\because \lim _{x \rightarrow 0} \frac{\tan x-\sin x}{a \sin ^{3} x}&amp;=\frac{1}{a} \lim _{x \rightarrow 0} \frac{\tan (1-\cos x)}{x^{3}}\\
&amp; =\frac{1}{a} \lim _{x \rightarrow 0} \frac{x \cdot \frac{1}{2} x^{2}}{x^{3}}=\frac{1}{2 a}=1, \\
\therefore a &amp; =\frac{1}{2} .
\end{aligned}
\lt/me\gt</p>

<p>当  <m>x \rightarrow 0</m> 时, <m>\frac{2}{3}(\cos x-\cos 2 x)</m> 是  <m>x^{2}</m>  的 [ D ].</p>

<p>(A) 高阶无穷小;
(B) 同阶但非等价无穷小;
(C) 低阶无穷小;
(D) 等价无穷小.</p>

<p>解 
\ltme\gt\begin{aligned}
    \because \lim _{x \rightarrow 0} \frac{\frac{2}{3}(\cos x-\cos 2 x)}{x^{2}}&amp;=\frac{2}{3} \lim _{x \rightarrow 0} \frac{\cos x-\cos ^{2} x+\sin ^{2} x}{x^{2}}\\
&amp;=\frac{2}{3}\left[\lim _{x \rightarrow 0}\left(\cos x \frac{1-\cos x}{x^{2}}\right)+\lim _{x \rightarrow 0} \frac{\sin ^{2} x}{x^{2}}\right]\\&amp;=\frac{2}{3}\left(\frac{1}{2}+1\right)=1,
\end{aligned}\lt/me\gt</p>

<p><m>\therefore</m> 等价.</p>

<p>求 <m>\displaystyle \lim _{x \rightarrow 0} \cot x\left(\frac{1}{\sin x}-\frac{1}{x}\right) </m>.</p>

<p>解：
\ltme\gt
\begin{aligned}
 \lim _{x \rightarrow 0} \cot x\left(\frac{1}{\sin x}-\frac{1}{x}\right)&amp;=\lim_{x \rightarrow 0} \frac{1}{\tan x} \frac{x-\sin x}{x \sin x}=\lim _{x \rightarrow 0} \frac{x-\sin x}{x^{3}} \\
&amp;\xlongequal{\frac{0}{0}} \lim_{x \rightarrow 0} \frac{1-\cos x}{3 x^{2}}=\lim _{x \rightarrow 0} \frac{\frac{x^{2}}{2}}{3 x^{2}}=\frac{1}{6} .
\end{aligned}
\lt/me\gt</p>

<p>求 <m>\displaystyle\lim _{t \rightarrow 0}\left(\frac{2}{\ln (1+t)}-\frac{2}{t}\right)</m>.</p>

<p>解
\ltme\gt
\begin{aligned}
\lim _{t \rightarrow 0}\left(\frac{2}{\ln (1+t)}-\frac{2}{t}\right) &amp;\xlongequal{\infty-\infty}\lim _{t \rightarrow 0} \frac{2[t-\ln (1+t)]}{t \ln (1+t)} \\
&amp;=\lim _{t \rightarrow 0} \frac{2[t-\ln (1+t)]}{t^{2}} \xlongequal{\frac{0}{0}} \lim _{t \rightarrow 0} \frac{2\left[1-\frac{1}{1+t}\right]}{2 t}\\&amp;=\lim _{t \rightarrow 0} \frac{1}{1+t}=1 .
\end{aligned}
\lt/me\gt</p>

<p>求 <m>\displaystyle \lim _{x \rightarrow 0} \frac{\tan x-\sin x}{\sin ^{3} x}</m>.</p>

<p>解 \ltme\gt\lim _{x \rightarrow 0} \frac{\tan x-\sin x}{\sin ^{3} x}=\lim _{x \rightarrow 0} \frac{\tan x(1-\cos x)}{x^{3}}=\lim _{x \rightarrow 0} \frac{1-\cos x}{x^{2}}=\frac{1}{2} \lt/me\gt</p>

<p><m>\displaystyle\lim _{x \rightarrow 0} \frac{\mathrm{e}^{2 x}-\mathrm{e}^{-3 x}}{\sqrt{1-x}-1} </m></p>

<p>解：
\ltme\gt\lim _{x \rightarrow 0} \frac{\mathrm{e}^{2 x}-\mathrm{e}^{-3 x}}{\sqrt{1-x}-1}=\lim _{x \rightarrow 0} \frac{\mathrm{e}^{-3 x}\left(\mathrm{e}^{5 x}-1\right)}{\frac{1}{2}(-x)}
=\lim _{x \rightarrow 0} \frac{\mathrm{e}^{-3 x} \cdot 5 x}{-\frac{1}{2} x}=-10 \lim _{x \rightarrow 0} \mathrm{e}^{-3 x}=-10 \times 1=-10 .\lt/me\gt</p>

<p>另解</p>

<p>\ltme\gt\lim _{x \rightarrow 0} \frac{\mathrm{e}^{2 x}-\mathrm{e}^{-3 x}}{\sqrt{1-x}-1}=\lim _{x \rightarrow 0} \frac{\left(\mathrm{e}^{2 x}-1\right)-\left(\mathrm{e}^{-3 x}-1\right)}{\frac{1}{2}(-x)}=\lim _{x \rightarrow 0} \frac{2 x-(-3 x)}{\frac{1}{2}(-x)}=\lim _{x \rightarrow 0} \frac{5 x}{\frac{1}{2}(-x)}=-10\lt/me\gt</p>

<p>(1)求 <m>\displaystyle \lim _{x \rightarrow 0}\left(\frac{1}{x} \ln \sqrt{\frac{1+x}{1-x}}\right)</m>;</p>

<p>(2)求 <m>\displaystyle \lim _{x \rightarrow 0} \frac{\mathrm{e}^{x}-\mathrm{e}^{\sin x}}{x-\sin x}</m>.</p>

<p>解(1)
\ltme\gt
\begin{aligned}
\lim _{x \rightarrow 0}\left(\frac{1}{x} \ln \sqrt{\frac{1+x}{1-x}}\right)&amp;=\frac{1}{2} \lim _{x \rightarrow 0} \frac{\ln (1+x)-\ln (1-x)}{x} \\
&amp;=\frac{1}{2}\left[\lim _{x \rightarrow 0} \frac{\ln (1+x)}{x}-\lim _{x \rightarrow 0} \frac{\ln (1-x)}{x}\right]\\&amp;=\frac{1}{2}[1-(-1)]=1
\end{aligned}
\lt/me\gt
 (2)
\ltme\gt
\begin{aligned}
\lim _{x \rightarrow 0} \frac{\mathrm{e}^{x}-\mathrm{e}^{\sin x}}{x-\sin x} &amp; =\lim _{x \rightarrow 0} \frac{\mathrm{e}^{\sin x}\left(\mathrm{e}^{x-\sin x}-1\right)}{x-\sin x}=\lim _{x \rightarrow 0} \frac{\mathrm{e}^{\sin x}(x-\sin x)}{x-\sin x} \\
&amp; =\lim _{x \rightarrow 0} \mathrm{e}^{\sin x}=\mathrm{e}^{0}=1
\end{aligned}
\lt/me\gt</p>

<p>求 <m>\displaystyle\lim _{x \rightarrow 0}\left(\frac{2+e^{\frac{1}{x}}}{1+e^{\frac{4}{x}}}+\frac{\sin x}{|x|}\right) </m>.</p>

<p>解:
\ltme\gt
\begin{aligned}
&amp;\lim _{x \rightarrow 0^{+}}\left(\frac{2+e^{\frac{1}{x}}}{1+e^{\frac{4}{x}}}+\frac{\sin x}{|x|}\right)=\lim _{x \rightarrow 0^{+}}\left(\frac{2 e^{-\frac{4}{x}}+e^{-\frac{3}{x}}}{e^{-\frac{4}{x}}+1}+\frac{\sin x}{x}\right)=1 \\
&amp;\lim _{x \rightarrow 0^{-}}\left(\frac{2+e^{\frac{1}{x}}}{1+e^{\frac{4}{x}}}+\frac{\sin x}{|x|}\right)=\lim _{x \rightarrow 0^{-}}\left(\frac{2+e^{\frac{1}{x}}}{1+e^{\frac{4}{x}}}-\frac{\sin x}{x}\right)=1
\end{aligned}
\lt/me\gt</p>

