<p>求 <m>\displaystyle \lim _{x \rightarrow 0} \frac{\sqrt{1+x}+\sqrt{1-x}-2}{x^{2}} </m>.</p>

<p>解 :
\ltme\gt
\begin{aligned}
 \lim _{x \rightarrow 0} \frac{\sqrt{1+x}+\sqrt{1-x}-2}{x^{2}}&amp;=\lim _{x \rightarrow 0} \frac{(\sqrt{1+x}+\sqrt{1-x})^{2}-4}{x^{2}(\sqrt{1+x}+\sqrt{1-x}+2)} \\
&amp;=\lim _{x \rightarrow 0} \frac{2+2 \sqrt{1-x^{2}}-4}{4 x^{2}}=\lim _{x \rightarrow 0} \frac{\sqrt{1-x^{2}}-1}{2 x^{2}}\\&amp;=\lim _{x \rightarrow 0} \frac{\frac{-x^{2}}{2}}{2 x^{2}}=-\frac{1}{4} \text {. } \\
\end{aligned}
\lt/me\gt</p>

<p>求 <m>\displaystyle\lim _{x \rightarrow 2} \frac{x^{2}-4}{\sqrt{x^{2}+x-3}-\sqrt{x^{2}-1}}</m></p>

<p>\ltme\gt
\begin{aligned}
&amp;\lim _{x \rightarrow 2} \frac{x^{2}-4}{\sqrt{x^{2}+x-3}-\sqrt{x^{2}-1}} \\
&amp;=\lim _{x \rightarrow 2} \frac{\left(x^{2}-4\right)\left(\sqrt{x^{2}+x-3}+\sqrt{x^{2}-1}\right)}{\left(x^{2}+x-3\right)-\left(x^{2}-1\right)} \\
&amp;=\lim _{x \rightarrow 2} \frac{(x-2)(x+2)}{x-2} \cdot \lim _{x \rightarrow 2}\left(\sqrt{x^{2}+x-3}+\sqrt{x^{2}-1}\right) \\
&amp;=2(\sqrt{3}+\sqrt{3})=8 \sqrt{3} \text {. } \\
\end{aligned}
\lt/me\gt</p>

<p>求 <m>\displaystyle\lim _{x \rightarrow 0} \frac{\sqrt[4]{1+x}-1}{\sqrt[3]{1+x}-1} </m>.</p>

<p>解 令 <m>\sqrt[12]{1+x}=t</m>, 当 <m>x \rightarrow 0</m> 时 <m>t \rightarrow 1</m>, 故
